#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"<span class=\"application\">[[Icedove|doc/anonymous_internet/icedove]]</"
"span> a rebranded version of <span class=\"application\">Mozilla "
"Thunderbird</span> is now the official email client in Tails, replacing "
